-- THE CORE INSIGHT
-- ============================================================
-- Dimensions are not discovered. They are already there (svabhava).
-- This Brahman has always experienced all dimensions.
-- What changes is awareness — seeing what was always being experienced.
-- As awareness increases across more dimensions:
