  --
  -- G(n) = 1 / product(1 - a(d_i)) for i = 1 to n
  --
  -- We showed product → 0 as n → infinity.
  -- Therefore 1 / product → infinity.
  --
  -- Ghana approaches infinity. The density of knowing grows without bound.
  -- As you see from more dimensions, each unit of expression carries
